author: rich
msg: Minor change to make TestRecorder avoid comparing the recorded request URI to the playback request URI.  This is not a valid thing to do, since the Servlet spec doesn't guarantee that they are the same.  Specifically, they can be different when the Servlet container interprets a welcome-file request.
